{"tid":2286584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共和黨州議員拒插手轉選舉人","createTime":"2020-11-15T06:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T06:54:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e796d7318bc59b390e6b7ef6be45bdbe595b410","tid":2286584,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201115/WDA7OKTIPBANTBN5VZYLZ62FIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201115%2FWDA7OKTIPBANTBN5VZYLZ62FIM%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=76498360\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201115%2FWDA7OKTIPBANTBN5VZYLZ62FIM%2F&h=2c6afaea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201115/WDA7OKTIPBANTBN5VZYLZ62FIM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n共和黨州議員拒插手轉選舉人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U9jRxkduw4S2LVkM1K9F-GW8U_Q=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CZR5NOHMYFFANJ42ZGOVCZEAUI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU9jRxkduw4S2LVkM1K9F-GW8U_Q%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCZR5NOHMYFFANJ42ZGOVCZEAUI.jpg&h=27e1b3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■拜登支持者揮舞有拜登肖像的旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n美國有共和黨人被指擬推動議會由該黨控制的州不理投票結果，推舉支持總統特朗普的選舉人，但多個關鍵州的州議員已明言拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：記招沒再提舞弊 「不知誰領下屆政府」特朗普接近認輸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憂牴觸民眾意向<br />\n<br />\n美國憲法列明，州議會有權決定其州最終提交的選舉人，但大多數州都已立法將權力交給選民，只有選舉結果因「選舉舞弊」等潛在原因到下月底期限前仍未明朗時，州議會才有機會介入，屆時亞利桑那、密歇根、賓夕法尼亞和威斯康辛四個爭持激烈、而且議會由共和黨控制州分或可宣佈特朗普勝出，推舉支持他的選舉人。<br />\n<br />\n不過，上述四州的共和黨州議員已表明無意插手，稱看不到任何選舉詐騙令他們要轉換選舉人，部份議員亦考慮到此舉會牴觸州法律和民眾意向。選舉專家也認為大選結果並非不清楚，國土安全部亦指這屆選舉是「美國史上最安全」，令州議會難有理據推翻民眾的投票結果。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：三州訴訟被駁回 律師樓退出<br />\n<br />\n以此方法改變大選結果成功機會其實不高，因為即使州議會願意不顧點票結果提交支持特朗普的選舉人，由民主黨控制的聯邦眾議院也可拒絕承認。若到明年1月20日眾院與由共和黨控制的聯邦參議院未能解決這紛爭，總統之位都只會由眾院議長、即民主黨人暫代，未見得對特朗普有好處。<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"7a937f4d51f3e6e802c1b076095defbcf7f43417","tid":2286584,"uid":286897,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afdd982cd7a156bda3169a8b63a93a33cd11d57e","tid":2286584,"uid":7484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:35:21.000Z","msg":"心急了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d189916ff0a90c288f7b3849554b04cb8a157f5","tid":2286584,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:35:54.000Z","msg":"又眾叛親離<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f85742b2309655575379708827bca81834556ba","tid":2286584,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:43:56.000Z","msg":"咁分析又情感投射  e d叫時事評論  唔係叫報導"},{"pid":"5a019663d378143c17be24324cd9d332c83c711e","tid":2286584,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"史上最安全（好似係）<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/orijonal/status/1327277595583414274?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Forijonal%2Fstatus%2F1327277595583414274%3Fs%3D21&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=fe68cec2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Forijonal%2Fstatus%2F1327277595583414274%3Fs%3D21&h=0ac6562a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/orijonal/status/1327277595583414274?s=21</a>"}]}